# Sky Scrapper API key from RapidAPI (free tier: 100 requests/month).
# Sign up at: https://rapidapi.com/apiheya/api/sky-scrapper
# Subscribe to the BASIC (free) plan, then copy your X-RapidAPI-Key.
# Leave unset to run in DEMO mode (no API calls, realistic fake prices).
SKY_SCRAPPER_API_KEY=

# Optional: override RapidAPI host (default: sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com)
# RAPIDAPI_HOST=sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com

# Optional: path to the local SQLite database.
# Defaults to flights.db in the project root.
# FLIGHT_DB_PATH=/absolute/path/to/flights.db
